name: Area Y: Yester Hill
caption: By day or night, stretching up to the limits of vision, the edges of my realm are marked by a great wall of mist. I was there at its birth.
description: The druids who worship Strahd as lord of the land and master of the weather convene here, atop Yester Hill, on the very edge of Strahdâ€™s domain. This hill is also where the evil blights that walk the Svalich Woods are born, and where Strahd comes on occasion to glimpse his ancestral home.
